strings: <voice_0x01000A6A><se_def>masterly: Wait here! This is a family affair. This woman will immediately take care of you.
<voice_0x01000A6B><se_high>the beautiful rose: I want to ask Jessica again.
<voice_0x01000A6C><se_high>the beautiful rose: You won't regret that, right? do not cry in front of your brother
<voice_0x01000A6D><se_high>Accuracy: not yet. Of course it's sad! I don't think it should be said!
<voice_0x01000A6E><se_high>Accuracy: But you can only think of family traditions and obligations! I say revenge for his murder!
<voice_0x01000A6F><se_high>the beautiful rose: The rematch...?
<voice_0x01000A70><se_high>the beautiful rose: Stop nonsense now! You are a woman and not a soldier!
<voice_0x01000A71><se_high>the beautiful rose: Do you think this is really what Alistair wants? You will mourn your sister's death like a real woman! this is our family
<voice_0x01000A72><se_high>Accuracy: No matter how you spend your family day at home!
<voice_0x01000A73><se_high>Accuracy: Alistair said<:> Believe it or not<:> Meaning<:> I told you to follow your heart.
<voice_0x01000A74><se_high>Accuracy: So I decided not to worry about the results. If you kill Alistair's killer, I'll pay you.
<voice_0x01000A75>the beautiful rose: ......
<voice_0x01000A76><se_high>the beautiful rose: skirt. It's like nobody's talking to you. Do whatever you want.
<voice_0x01000A77><se_high>the beautiful rose: does not include...
<voice_0x01000A78><se_high>the beautiful rose: Enough with the girls! This house must be evacuated immediately!
<voice_0x01000A79><se_high>Accuracy: Yeah, I keep going until I find out.
<voice_0x01000A7A><se_high>Accuracy: it is better! add! Leave me alone, I'm going to!
<voice_0x01000A7B><se_high>Accuracy: Sorry I didn't tell the truth earlier. I'm not happy
<voice_0x01000A7C><se_high>Reflections: Jessica, are you really going?
<voice_0x01000A7D><se_high>Accuracy: I want you to take care of this city while I am away.
<voice_0x01000A7E><se_high>Accuracy: Alistair answered "yes". He says you will protect the village and become a famous warrior.
<voice_0x01000A7F><se_high>sweet potato: (Flip it, feel it...! Feel it...)

<voice_0x01000A81><se_high>Accuracy: Your job of spying on my room is over. Now patrol!
<voice_0x01000A82><se_high>Reflections: I have heard!
